 mouse">Executable File</span><img src=images/executable.jpg alt="Executable File"></a></div><div class=p>You can run the Windows installer with a few options to customise the software for what you need. Additionally, it will add the program to the PATH environmental variable so that the tools are available from the command line.</div></div></section><?php include "../footer.php" ?></script><?php include "../scripts.php" ?></html>`